  "3031890": {
    "name": "Acts of Blood",
    "steam_appid": 3031890,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/bf3087af72e31a10697496f0ca2b736e.avif?t=1765672685\" width=550 height=219 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PLOT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the bustling city of Bandapa, Hendra's life torn apart when his family is slain by his father's business rival. Left alone and seeking justice, the college law student finds no help from the corrupt legal system that protects the killers. Discovering a powerful group behind the attack, Hendra decides to take revenge himself, determined to make them pay for their actions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/fdeef9a38c29cebce0ce46e40eb707a8.poster.avif?t=1765672685\" width=602 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/fdeef9a38c29cebce0ce46e40eb707a8.webm?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/fdeef9a38c29cebce0ce46e40eb707a8.mp4?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will play as the protagonist, Hendra. Engaging in fast-paced, hand-to-hand combat against waves of enemies across various levels. The objective is to defeat all foes, including powerful boss characters on each level, using brutal combat movements, various melee &amp; firearm weapons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dynamic Brutal Combat</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamic Brutal Combat ensures intense, visceral fights with fluid chains of bone-crushing attacks, blocks, and counters. Realistic enemy reactions and gruesome finishers keep combat brutally engaging, adapting to fast-paced, blood-soaked scenarios.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/59c2c600aa2053a753d67ff30a5288c6.poster.avif?t=1765672685\" width=602 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/59c2c600aa2053a753d67ff30a5288c6.webm?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/59c2c600aa2053a753d67ff30a5288c6.mp4?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Various Melee &amp; Firearm Weapons</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The game features a diverse arsenal of vicious melee and powerful firearm weapons. Players can switch between bats, knives, pistols, and rifles, delivering brutal beatdowns and bloody headshots, experimenting to find the most devastating tools for different enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/def49de45fcad2c86050f1eaf9838354.poster.avif?t=1765672685\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/def49de45fcad2c86050f1eaf9838354.webm?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/def49de45fcad2c86050f1eaf9838354.mp4?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Destructible Environmental Elements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Destructible Environmental Elements add realism and strategy to combat. Players can shatter furniture, and use props as weapons, making fights unpredictably chaotic and allowing for creative, ruthless tactical approaches.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/de42a389277e8403f077a45684bb3594.poster.avif?t=1765672685\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/de42a389277e8403f077a45684bb3594.webm?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/de42a389277e8403f077a45684bb3594.mp4?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Traditional Parkour</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Traditional Parkour mechanics provide fluid movement and dynamic, escapes. Players can run, jump, and climb through levels, seamlessly integrating agility into combat for strategic positioning and surprise attacks.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/8079bd3144c5cbd548f475a9fbd288ef.poster.avif?t=1765672685\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/8079bd3144c5cbd548f475a9fbd288ef.webm?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/8079bd3144c5cbd548f475a9fbd288ef.mp4?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Outfit Customization</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Personalize Hendra’s look with a selection of outfits available in his apartment wardrobe. Unlock new styles and switch up his appearance to match your vibe or mission needs, adding an extra layer of immersion to each stage of the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/3e68eb5e1c502d2c7a84ec79c64973f8.poster.avif?t=1765672685\" width=602 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/3e68eb5e1c502d2c7a84ec79c64973f8.webm?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3031890/extras/3e68eb5e1c502d2c7a84ec79c64973f8.mp4?t=1765672685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
